quests.desc: Welcome to TextWorld! First off, if it's not too much trouble, I need you to try to head east. With that done, pick up the sock from the stand within the garage. And then, you can place the sock into the locker. Got that? Good!

infos.name: garage
infos.desc:
You are in a garage. A normal one.

 You make out [if c_0 is locked]a locked[else if c_0 is open]an opened[otherwise]a closed[end if] locker close by.[if c_0 is open and there is something in the c_0] The locker contains [a list of things in the c_0]. Now that's what I call TextWorld![end if][if c_0 is open and the c_0 contains nothing] What a letdown! The locker is empty![end if] You can see a stand. What a coincidence, weren't you just thinking about a stand? [if there is something on the s_0]On the stand you can see [a list of things on the s_0]. I mean, just wow! Isn't TextWorld just the best?[end if][if there is nothing on the s_0]However, the stand, like an empty stand, has nothing on it. What, you think everything in TextWorld should have stuff on it?[end if]

There is an unguarded exit to the west.

infos.name: shower
infos.desc:
Look around you. Take it all in. It's not every day someone gets to be in a shower. I guess you better just go and list everything you see here.



You don't like doors? Why not try going east, that entranceway is unguarded. You don't like doors? Why not try going south, that entranceway is unblocked.

infos.name: sauna
infos.desc:
You've entered a sauna.



There is an unblocked exit to the north.

infos.name: locker
infos.desc: The locker looks strong, and impossible to crack. [if open]It is open.[else if closed]It is closed.[otherwise]It is locked.[end if]

infos.name: banana
infos.desc: You couldn't pay me to eat that ordinary thing.

objective: I hope you're ready to go into rooms and interact with objects, because you've just entered TextWorld! Here is your task for today. First thing I need you to do is to head east. Then, retrieve the sock from the stand. Then, insert the sock into the locker in the garage. Once that's all handled, you can stop!
